{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "olaf-s-funniest-moments",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GJY4NrlbGzc&t=3s",
    "mode": "cues_rebuild"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The following contains clips from Disney's Frozen 2, now available on Blueray and DVD",
      "zh": "以下包含迪士尼《冰雪奇緣2》的片段，現已在藍光和DVD發行",
      "ja": "以下はディズニーの『アナと雪の女王2』のクリップを含みます。ブルーレイとDVDで発売中",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, okay, um, I'm Lion, grizzly bear, a monster, out of here, angry, fake bear",
      "zh": "啊，好，嗯，我是獅子、灰熊、怪物，離開這裡，生氣，假熊",
      "ja": "ああ、はい、えっと、私はライオン、グリズリーベア、モンスター、ここから出る、怒ってる、偽のクマ",
      "time": "00:00:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ah, hunt!",
      "zh": "啊，狩獵！",
      "ja": "ああ、狩り！",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm on Team Mobile Monster.",
      "zh": "我在行動怪物隊。",
      "ja": "私はチームモバイルモンスターにいる。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tardis mistake of your life.",
      "zh": "你人生中最大的錯誤。",
      "ja": "あなたの人生最大の過ちだ。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wouldn't even kiss you!",
      "zh": "甚至不會親你！",
      "ja": "君にキスもしないよ！",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Villain!",
      "zh": "壞蛋！",
      "ja": "悪役！",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, we all kind of got it.",
      "zh": "哦，我們都有點明白了。",
      "ja": "ああ、みんななんとなくわかった。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, all off, you're up.",
      "zh": "好了，全下來，你上場。",
      "ja": "よし、みんな下がって、君の番だ。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So much easier now that I can read.",
      "zh": "現在我會讀書了，簡單多了。",
      "ja": "読めるようになってずっと楽になった。",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lightning round, boys against girls.",
      "zh": "快問快答，男生對女生。",
      "ja": "ライトニングラウンド、男子対女子。",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm ready, I'm ready.",
      "zh": "我準備好了，我準備好了。",
      "ja": "準備できた、準備できた。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Go.",
      "zh": "開始。",
      "ja": "行け。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Unicorn, ice cream, castle, open,",
      "zh": "獨角獸，冰淇淋，城堡，開放，",
      "ja": "ユニコーン、アイスクリーム、城、開け、",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Teapot, mouse, oh, Elsa!",
      "zh": "茶壺，老鼠，哦，艾莎！",
      "ja": "ティーポット、ネズミ、おお、エルサ！",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think Olaf should get to rearrange.",
      "zh": "我覺得奧拉夫不應該重新排列。",
      "ja": "オラフに並べ替えさせるべきじゃないと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Doesn't matter, this is going to be a stitch.",
      "zh": "沒關係，這會很有趣。",
      "ja": "関係ない、これは面白くなるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Two sisters, one mind.",
      "zh": "兩姐妹，一心。",
      "ja": "二人の姉妹、一つの心。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, here we go.",
      "zh": "好了，開始了。",
      "ja": "よし、始めよう。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You got this Elsa.",
      "zh": "你行的，艾莎。",
      "ja": "エルサ、君ならできる。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anytime, just do it with your body.",
      "zh": "隨時，只要用身體做就行。",
      "ja": "いつでも、体でやればいい。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "zh": "沒什麼。",
      "ja": "何もない。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Air, treat, people, triple.",
      "zh": "空氣，請客，人，三倍。",
      "ja": "空気、ごちそう、人、三倍。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's not a word.",
      "zh": "那不是一個詞。",
      "ja": "それは言葉じゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, shovel boy.",
      "zh": "喔，鏟子男孩。",
      "ja": "ああ、シャベルボーイ。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Teeth? Oh, do in the dishes.",
      "zh": "牙齒？喔，洗碗。",
      "ja": "歯？ああ、皿洗い。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Followed bear!",
      "zh": "跟著熊！",
      "ja": "熊に続け！",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "zh": "嘿。",
      "ja": "ねえ。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry, I'm tired too.",
      "zh": "抱歉，我也累了。",
      "ja": "ごめん、私も疲れた。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And Sven promised to read me a bedtime story.",
      "zh": "而且斯文答應要給我讀睡前故事。",
      "ja": "それにスヴェンが寝る前の話を読んでくれるって約束した。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you, Sven?",
      "zh": "你答應了嗎，斯文？",
      "ja": "約束したかい、スヴェン？",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Dude, are you?",
      "zh": "老兄，你是？",
      "ja": "おい、君は？",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, you should do the best voices.",
      "zh": "喔，你應該做最棒的配音。",
      "ja": "ああ、最高の声を出すべきだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like when you pretend to be crisp up in your life.",
      "zh": "就像你假裝自己很酷一樣。",
      "ja": "まるで人生でカリッとしてるふりをするみたいに。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just need to go talk to some rocks about my childhood.",
      "zh": "我只是需要去跟一些石頭談談我的童年。",
      "ja": "ちょっと子供時代のことで岩に話しかけに行く必要がある。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Um, how about you guys start without me?",
      "zh": "嗯，你們先開始吧，不用等我。",
      "ja": "えっと、君たち先に始めてていいよ？",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am okay.",
      "zh": "我沒事。",
      "ja": "私は大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you know that water has memory?",
      "zh": "你知道水有記憶嗎？",
      "ja": "水には記憶があるって知ってた？",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "True fact, it's disputed by many, but it's true.",
      "zh": "這是真的，雖然很多人有爭議，但是真的。",
      "ja": "事実だよ、多くの人が疑ってるけど、本当だ。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you know men are six times more likely to be struck by lightning?",
      "zh": "你知道男性被雷擊的機率是女性的六倍嗎？",
      "ja": "男性は雷に打たれる確率が女性の6倍だって知ってた？",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you know Gorilla is burp when they're happy?",
      "zh": "你知道大猩猩快樂時會打嗝嗎？",
      "ja": "ゴリラは嬉しいときにゲップをするって知ってた？",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you know we blink four million times a day?",
      "zh": "你知道我們一天眨眼四百萬次嗎？",
      "ja": "私たちは一日に400万回まばたきするって知ってた？",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you know why I'm that poofed squares?",
      "zh": "你知道為什麼我那麼蓬鬆嗎？",
      "ja": "なぜ私があんなにふわふわしてるか知ってた？",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you know sleeping quietly on long journeys, prevents insanity?",
      "zh": "你知道長途旅行中安靜睡覺可以防止瘋狂嗎？",
      "ja": "長旅で静かに眠ることが狂気を防ぐって知ってた？",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha.",
      "zh": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈。",
      "ja": "はははははははは。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, that's not true.",
      "zh": "是啊，那不是真的。",
      "ja": "うん、それは本当じゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is.",
      "zh": "是真的。",
      "ja": "本当だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's definitely true.",
      "zh": "絕對是真的。",
      "ja": "絶対に本当だ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's the truth.",
      "zh": "這是真相。",
      "ja": "それが真実だ。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, that was unanimous, but I will look it up when we get home.",
      "zh": "嗯，這是全票通過，但我回家會查證。",
      "ja": "まあ、全会一致だったけど、家に帰ったら調べるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They're both asleep.",
      "zh": "他們兩個都睡著了。",
      "ja": "二人とも眠っている。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So, what do you want to do?",
      "zh": "那麼，你想做什麼？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、何をしたい？",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sven, keep a steady.",
      "zh": "斯文，保持穩定。",
      "ja": "スヴェン、安定させて。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Will ya?",
      "zh": "可以嗎？",
      "ja": "お願いね？",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いや。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anna?",
      "zh": "安娜？",
      "ja": "アナ？",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna?",
      "zh": "安娜？",
      "ja": "アナ？",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Remember our first trip like this when I said you'd have to be crazy",
      "zh": "還記得我們第一次這樣旅行時我說你得瘋了",
      "ja": "こんな旅は初めてで、君は狂ってるに違いないと言ったのを覚えてる？",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "to want to marry a man you just met.",
      "zh": "想嫁給一個剛認識的男人。",
      "ja": "会ったばかりの男と結婚したいなんて。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait, what?",
      "zh": "等等，什麼？",
      "ja": "え、何？",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Crazy?",
      "zh": "瘋了？",
      "ja": "狂ってる？",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You didn't say I was crazy.",
      "zh": "你沒說我瘋了。",
      "ja": "君は私が狂ってるとは言わなかった。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You think I'm crazy?",
      "zh": "你覺得我瘋了嗎？",
      "ja": "私が狂ってると思う？",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did.",
      "zh": "我有說。",
      "ja": "言ったよ。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You were.",
      "zh": "你是。",
      "ja": "君はそうだった。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not crazy.",
      "zh": "不是瘋了。",
      "ja": "狂ってはいない。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Clearly.",
      "zh": "很明顯。",
      "ja": "明らかに。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just naive.",
      "zh": "只是天真。",
      "ja": "ただの純粋さ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Not naive.",
      "zh": "不是天真。",
      "ja": "純粋じゃない。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just, just new to love.",
      "zh": "只是，剛開始懂愛。",
      "ja": "ただ、恋愛に不慣れなだけ。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like, like, I was.",
      "zh": "就像，我曾經是。",
      "ja": "まるで、私がそうだったように。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And when you're new, you're bound to get it wrong.",
      "zh": "當你新手時，難免會犯錯。",
      "ja": "初心者の時は間違えるものだ。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So you're saying, I'm wrong for you.",
      "zh": "所以你是說，我不適合你。",
      "ja": "つまり、君は私に合わないと言いたいの？",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, no.",
      "zh": "不，不。",
      "ja": "いや、違う。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna?",
      "zh": "安娜？",
      "ja": "アナ？",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Elsa?",
      "zh": "艾莎？",
      "ja": "エルサ？",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sven?",
      "zh": "斯文？",
      "ja": "スヴェン？",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Samantha?",
      "zh": "薩曼莎？",
      "ja": "サマンサ？",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't even know if Samantha.",
      "zh": "我甚至不知道薩曼莎是否存在。",
      "ja": "サマンサがいるかどうかも知らない。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hahaha.",
      "zh": "哈哈哈。",
      "ja": "ははは。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's normal.",
      "zh": "那很正常。",
      "ja": "それは普通だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why does that soldier look so familiar?",
      "zh": "為什麼那個士兵看起來這麼眼熟？",
      "ja": "あの兵士はなぜこんなに見覚えがあるんだ？",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lieutenant, get the sword!",
      "zh": "中尉，拿劍來！",
      "ja": "中尉、剣を持ってこい！",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That was magic.",
      "zh": "那是魔法。",
      "ja": "あれは魔法だった。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you see that?",
      "zh": "你看到了嗎？",
      "ja": "見たか？",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course I saw it.",
      "zh": "當然看到了。",
      "ja": "もちろん見たよ。",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Will you chose a nice cold greeting?",
      "zh": "你會選擇一個冷淡的問候嗎？",
      "ja": "冷たい挨拶を選ぶのか？",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They've been trapped in here this whole time.",
      "zh": "他們一直被困在這裡。",
      "ja": "彼らはずっとここに閉じ込められている。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do we do now?",
      "zh": "我們現在該怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "今どうする？",
